Travis-CI - Deploy shinyapps.io
========================================================


   `build.R` 

```
#! /usr/bin/env Rscript 

shinyapps::setAccountInfo(name='kurtharriger',
                          token='DE3CF8C226BDB4F14DBC429AFB12403B',
                          secret=Sys.getenv("SHINYAPPS_SECRET"))
shinyapps::deployApp('shiny')

```


Travis-CI - Deploy shinyapps.io
========================================================

   `.travis.yml` 

```
language: r
sudo: required
script: ./build.R
SHINYAPPS_SECRET:
  secure: IY+WvEe5...MU3X6GU/yZFvQ=
```

